\id 2TH NT0051.2T1 ONO Phinnemore NOV-1990. 
\h 2 Tesalonaika 
\toc1 2 Tesalonaika 
\toc2 2 Tesalonaika 
\mt1 2 Tesalonaika  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Paulo, Sailas so Timoti ŋedo ŋei ŋerep doku tau tau magu, Tesalonaika matko gemami, Anutu Magak so Waom Yesu Kristo wane ŋei ŋerep, ŋinane kibi iwa qemaine.  
\v 2 Anutu Magak so Yesu Kristoŋo maine wet menaŋ so peam ŋiboniake.   
\s1 Kristo Yewao Wano Wanok Wakoniake Lotkeake  
\p
\v 3 Kimakop, naso baŋem ŋene ŋinane raŋem paki Anutu bakomine kito okanmaine. Ŋene iwa okanmaine, yemo mayakatne, onokawane ŋinane mali malipŋineŋo zok manerop suamaike, so wet maep ŋine bonep bonep yewaŋo doku tau tau magu okan nagukei, yewa mo zok kakapa suaine okanmaike.  
\v 4 Kine ea wane, ŋene ŋedom Anutu wane doku tau tau magu gemami, eŋane keueno ŋene ŋinane don kisi ra mawa ŋune okanmaine, ŋene ra edane mawaŋune okanmaine, yemo ŋaba edo masi worik okanŋunbi, ŋine wikile so wetborik korop geu paki, mali malipŋine mi qorodoŋgi soringeu paki, togogole malipke okoramami paki, umat so wikile kine kine korop teweke okoramami, ea wane.   
\p
\v 5 Iwa yemo Anutu wane wano wanok koboine, onoka wane kine korop iwa yalinane, ŋine baŋ gege togon Mat Uruminane kotino wake waket wane rokop maratkaikei wane ŋine wikile kutno gemami.  
\v 6 Anutuŋo detki koboine pamaike, ea wane rokop baŋ okanŋoniake, ŋine wikile ŋibonmami, ŋei yewa eŋe wikile eboniake.  
\v 7 Ŋo wikile detmami, ŋine yemo magunut ŋungi paki, ŋene yaleka okan ŋoniake, eŋe iwa baŋ okaniake yemo Waom Yesu eŋine lotkeake, naso yewao aŋelo magukoune zonominerop loutne eŋerop qeliwo ŋine sari okanŋoniake.  
\v 8 Gerep bolamgorop sariki paki Anutu mi detka okanmami, ŋei yewa so Waomze Yesu Kristo wane Don Maine yewa dere ŋadek okanmami ŋei yaline korop engu matalioniake.  
\v 9 Ŋei yewa eŋe turuŋine bori wori wane wikile togogole maratkau Waom kaitino ŋine so zonomine togogolane saraino, ŋine ebu mapok one biraongi arikei.  
\v 10 Eŋe sariake, Kaiwe Naso yewao yemo, ŋei ŋerep magukoune korop eŋano ŋine qeli ewe zonom mayakane, so mali malipkorop eŋanoŋine bakom mawa mawa mayakane, ŋine yaleka weneŋ eŋane keuo okorakei, onokawane ŋene don ŋidangone, yewa ŋine dere malipkakoi, ea wane.   
\p
\v 11 Kine iwa yale wane, ŋene naso baŋem ŋinane meŋenka okanmaine, ŋene Anutuze olatmaine, yemo ŋine gege gekeiwane raki paki, ŋidora newanŋunge, ea wane rokopko gekei wane, olat okanmaine, wane eŋe eŋine zonomŋo maine qesiŋŋungi, kine kine maine korop okangei wane wetkemami, yewa okanwarekei, paki mali malipŋinane urata wele maratka warekei.  
\v 12 Numa yaleoken okanbi, Waomze Yesu wane eŋetineŋo ŋine ŋibu wieake, ŋo ŋido eŋane eŋetine ma wiekei, iwa yemo Anutuze so Waomze Yesu Kristo qomine rarainane yale okan ŋuniake, ea ŋene ŋinane meŋenka okanmaine.   
\c 2  
\s1 Borikine Mama Ŋei Eŋe Wakone Ŋei Wet Masiuk Okanone Geki Yesu Lotkeake  
\p
\v 1 Kimakop, Waomze Yesu lotke lotkeinane so ŋenze eŋerop weneŋ maratnagu gege wane don iwa yale ŋidanmaile,  
\v 2 isi ŋei natne eŋe rakoi, Waom sariakane nasoine mo lotke more yuanŋunge, yale ra ŋidanbi ŋine ikopka wetŋineŋo misuk dere siukkei, me mi qisekei. Ŋinano ŋino ŋei natneŋo Asu wano more raikei, me ŋenane aŋao more ŋidanikei, me raikei edo kibiwo qe ŋebongoi, yale ŋidanikei.  
\v 3 Don kine kine yale, me yale ra isiŋunbi misuk desikei, Waom wane Naso ikopka mi bomileake, alakane miti Matali Qetali Mama Ŋei yewa wakone pakimo, Borikine Mama Ŋei eŋe gerep sorao wane biŋek, ketki zeakane didiwo wakoniake.  
\v 4 Eŋe baŋ ŋei eŋe yeye kine kine korop ea wane ra meŋenka okanmami, so ŋei eŋe yeye kine kine mayakatne ra okanmami, yewa ŋabaka wareake. Eŋe baŋ eŋine eŋetine mawa naguki paki, natne korop ebu ket biraoniake, paki Anutu wane Bakom Urumgo ari waketki paki pese mere eŋinane “na Anutu” rayake.   
\p
\v 5 Na ŋinerop gekole, yewao iwa wane mo korop ŋidan warekole, ŋine ea mi detmami me?  
\v 6 Ŋo iwa yemo wakonbe rakimo, kine kine maneŋo leŋkamaike, ea ŋine mo detkamami, nasoine pamaike, yewao yemo Borikine Mama Ŋei, yewa eŋe baŋ didiwo wakoniake.  
\v 7 Borikine eŋe urata mo sanka ma okanmaike, ŋo tanik daleo wakoniake, eamo ikop mi wakoniake. Eŋe paki ŋei mane maŋo mainkaki zinge okanmaike, ea maki masikaniake.  
\v 8 Pakimo Borikine Mama eŋe baŋ didiwo wakongimo, Waom Yesu wane Asuineŋo aŋaino ŋine baŋ saketki paki qeake, paki didiwo sari lotkeakane qeli ewe zonomineŋo qe kito pelekki siukeake.  
\v 9 Borikine Mama Ŋei yewa, eŋe baŋ Satan wane zonom yewarop sariake, paki masi kine kine togole mayake, so tanik kine kine isisine so qotkoine kuneŋine mayake.  
\v 10 So ŋei midakei wane biŋek gemami, eŋe borikine maikei wane, wet masiuk okanoniake, eŋe midakei yemo onoka wane mida, eŋe don wele dere mena menaŋ yewa ŋadekka okanmami, ea wane midakei.  
\v 11 Kine iwa yalinane, Anutuŋo liwe liwek wane zonom suaine talekaki ket more, ŋei eŋane keueno urata maki, eŋe isi don wele midaine yewa dere malipkaikei.  
\v 12 Ea wane weleine yemo ŋei korop don wele dere mi malipka okanmami, ŋo eŋe siluŋ borikine simile det okanmami, ŋo eŋe siluŋ borikinane simile det okanmami, eŋe turuŋine wikile maratkaikei.   
\s1 Anutuŋo Koso Ŋibuyakane Mo Ma Wakonŋunge  
\p
\v 13 Kimakop, ŋine Waomŋo wet maep okanŋun okanmaike, ŋene ea wane ŋinane Anutu naso baŋem bakomine kito okanmaine, Anutuŋo mokaka koso ŋibuyakane ma wakon ŋunge, yemo Asu wane zonomŋo ŋibuki Anutu wane ŋei ŋerep magu libe libe okangoi, so mali malipŋineŋo don wele dere malip kakoi, yale okangoi wane, Anutuŋo koso ŋibuke.  
\v 14 Ŋene don maine ŋidangone yewao, Anutuŋo ŋidora newan ŋunge, eŋe newan ŋunge, yemo ŋine Waomze Yesu Kristo wane qeli ewe zonom yewa welaine okane ma gekeiwane.  
\v 15 Eso ea wane kimakop, ŋine togogole okorau paki, don wele kito ŋibongone, aŋaŋo ŋidangone, me kibiwo qe ŋibongone, yewa malilipka okorakei.   
\p
\v 16 Waomze Yesu Kristo oŋom, so Anutu Magazeŋo wetmaep okan ŋonge, so eŋine wetne mayakakatnane wetpese papatogon yewa, ŋenane biŋek rake, ea toma kakenane ra ŋebonge.  
\v 17 Oŋo maine ŋinane kotoŋine maki qaeake, so ma togoleŋungi togole more urata maineka maikei, so don mayakatneka raikei.   
\c 3  
\s1 Ŋenane Meŋenkau Anutuŋo Qesiŋŋoniake  
\p
\v 1 Kimakop, ŋenane rau paki meŋenkau, Waom wane donŋo tako rakotka sua ariki qeli ewe zonomine ŋinane keu ŋino wakonge, yalewaka wakone ariake.  
\v 2 Eso koso yaleka meŋenkau, Anutuŋo ŋei borikine mama so tanik manikene qotkoine eŋane meteo ŋine makokŋoniake. Ŋei koropŋo Anutu wane don dere malipka mi okan okanmami.   
\p
\v 3 Ŋo Waom yemo raki togole togole, ea wane eŋe baŋ ma togoleŋuniake so wareŋungi, Ŋei Borikine Welaineŋo mi ŋibu teba ŋuniake.  
\v 4 So Waomŋo ŋinane raki paki wet pesek ŋebonmaike, ŋene detlukmaine yemo ŋene don ŋidanmaine, yewa ŋine dere ma okanmami, wane ŋene koso don ŋidanŋem ŋine baŋ dere takotke ma okane gekei.   
\p
\v 5 Waomŋo maine kotoŋine iwenkaki, Anutu wane wet maep yewa qeirop dere ketpi paki, Kristoŋo togogole okora umat teweke ŋebonge, yewa detluk kaikei.   
\s1 Urata Kitoqoke Qewoloŋ Ge More Miti Mage Mage Eamo Mi Pamaike  
\p
\v 6 Kimakop, Waomze Yesu Kristo wane eŋetko ŋene togoleka ŋidanŋem detpi, kimakopze doku tau tau magu natneŋo taboŋ qewoloŋ ge okanmami, eŋe ŋedo don kito edangone, yewa mi teweke mogare ge okanmami, ŋei yaline eŋe korop kakakŋone arikei.  
\v 7 Ŋine ŋidom kine mo detlukware mami, wane ŋene okangone ea wane rokopka ŋine okanikei, ŋene ŋinerop geŋem paki, taboŋ qewoloŋ mi gekone.  
\v 8 Ŋene ŋei mane wano ŋine sola qesiŋ mane lewine midaine mi omakakone, midakaka, oma kaikenane turuŋine yemo ŋene urata makone, so wikile detkone, kaiwe so ruo urata togogole makone paki, natne ŋine wikile urata mi ŋibonikenane, yale okangone.  
\v 9 Ŋene iwa okangone yemo, ŋene Aposolo ŋetne wesi aboŋ wane qesiŋ ŋonikenane raŋunŋem rap, ŋo ŋene ŋinano ŋine sola qesiŋ mane mi raŋunŋem ŋebongei yem midaka, ŋene iwa okangone, yemo ŋine ŋene okangone, yewa kau paki mogare, yalewaka okane gekeiwane numa sikan ŋungone.  
\v 10 Ŋene ŋinerop ge more, iwayale ŋidangone, “Ŋei mane urata mayakane bauine wakiso, ŋine ŋara misuk manbi neake!”   
\p
\v 11 Ŋene don iwa ramaine yemo onokawane, ŋene detŋem, ŋei natne eŋe ŋinane keu ŋino taboŋ qewoloŋ geokanmami, eŋe urata mane mi mama yaup ŋei natne eŋane uratao dongoka welaineŋo qole qole don sawaŋ rau paki, qeweloŋ geokanmami.  
\v 12 Ŋene Waom Yesu Kristo wane Pidon wane ŋei yewa togoleka edane more, girem don iwa yale edanŋem detlukkei, eŋe pese ketluke mere urata mau wele wakongi, enŋeno ŋine ma nekei.   
\p
\v 13 Ŋo kimakop, ŋine yemo siluŋ masi tanik maine okanikei wane, bauŋine misuk wayake.  
\v 14 Yewao ŋei maneŋo don korop kibiwo qe ŋibonmaine, iwa baŋ dere mi tewekeake, eŋe yale okangiso, ŋine kineine detkau paki, kine kine mane misuk okanka more qeliŋkau, eŋineka geake. Paki kineine dere baŋ gamukaki, wetine maingeake.  
\v 15 Ŋo ŋine ŋaba yale misuk okankaikei, ea wane turuŋine yemo kima ma more, girem don olasikei.   
\s1 Don Mosop Piwitne  
\p
\v 16 Waom eŋine, yemo ŋenane peam wane kine, oŋo naso baŋem peam maine ma wakone ŋiboniake paki, ŋinano rokopke ware payake, Waomŋo ŋinerop korop ge wareake.  
\v 17 Na Paulo, nae meteneŋo kibi piwitne iwa qe more, kaiwe maine ramaile. Kibi qe okanmaile, korop ea wane mete kibine iwa yale mot okanmaile.  
\v 18 Waomze Yesu Kristo wane mosopŋo ŋinano korop papa togon pawareake.   